quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  14,19,Hauoni here kuti zvirokwazvo Allah ndivo vakasika matenga nenyika zvechokwadi? Kana vakada vanokwanisa kukubvisai uye (pachinzvimbo chenyu) vounza chisikwa chitsva
  14,20,Uye kuna Allah izvi hazvivavomeri
  14,21,"Uye vose vachamira pamberi paAllah (pazuva rokutongwa), nokudaro avo vasina simba vachati kune avo vaizvitutumadza (madzimambo): “Zvirokwazvo, taitevera imi, saka munokwanisa here kutidzivirirawo chero nechii zvacho kubva kumarwadzo aAllah?” Vachati: “Dai Allah vakatipa gwara, dai takakutungamirirai. Zvakangofanana nesu (iyezvino) kushaya tarisiro, kana kutsungirira, hatina nzvimbo yokutizira.”"
  14,22,"Uye Satani achati kana nyaya yatongwa: “Zvirokwazvo, Allah vakakuvimbisai vimbiso yechokwadi. Uye neniwo ndikakuvimbisai, asi ndakakurasisai. Ndakanga ndisina simba pamusoro penyu kunze kwekuti ndakakudanai mukandidavira. Nokudaro musandinenedzere, asi zvinenedzerei pachenyu. Handikwanisi kukubatsirai, kana imi kundibatsirawo. Ndinoramba muitiro wenyu wakare wokundisanganisa naAllah (nekunditeerera muhupenyu hwepasi). Zvirokwazvo, kune mutongo wakaomarara kuvaiti vezvakaipa.”"
  14,23,"Uye kune avo vaitenda (muIslaam) nokuita mabasa akanaka, vachapinzwa muParadhiso iro rinoyerera mvura pasi paro, umo vachagara zvachose kuburikidza nekuda kwaTenzi vavo. Kumhoresana kwavo imomo kuchange kuri: “Salaam (Runyararo)!”"
  14,24,"Hauoni here kuti Allah vanopa sei muenzaniso? Shoko rakanaka rakafanana nemuti wakanaka, midzi yawo yakabatirira zvakanyanya, uye mapazi awo anobata denga"